flavor_text_entries.flavor_text:
Il peut paralyser l’ennemi d’un regard.
Il amplifie l’énergie du soleil dans
son corps.

It can stop its opponents’
movements with just a glare. It takes
in solar energy and boosts it internally.

Il garde la tête haute pour intimider
l’ennemi, et ne combat sérieusement
que les ennemis les plus puissants.

They raise their heads to intimidate
opponents but only give it their all
when fighting a powerful opponent.

It only gives its all against strong
opponents who are not fazed by the
glare from Serperior’s noble eyes.

It only gives its all against strong
opponents who are not fazed by the
glare from Serperior’s noble eyes.

ジャローダの　けだかい　ひとみで
いすくめられても　へいきな　つよい
あいてにだけ　ほんきを　だす。

샤로다의 고상한 눈동자로
쏘아보아도 태연할 정도로 강한
상대에게만 진정한 실력을 발휘한다.

Il ne donnera tout son potentiel que contre un
ennemi puissant indifférent à son regard écrasant
de noblesse.

Im Kampf zeigt es nur Gegnern, die seinem
edlen Blick standhalten, seine wahre Kraft.

Tan solo muestra su verdadero poder a quienes no se
amedrentan ante su noble pero inquisitoria mirada.

Dà il meglio di sé solo contro chi non resta
intimidito dal suo nobile sguardo.

It only gives its all against strong opponents who
are not fazed by the glare from Serperior’s
noble eyes.

ジャローダの　気高い　瞳で
射すくめられても　平気な　強い
相手にだけ　本気を　出す。

にらむだけで　あいての　うごきを
とめてしまう。たいようエネルギーを
たいないで　ぞうふくさせる。

째려보기만 해도 상대의 움직임을
멈추게 한다. 태양에너지를
체내에서 증폭시킨다.

Il peut paralyser l’ennemi d’un regard. Il amplifie
l’énergie du soleil dans son corps.

Bringt Gegner mit einem einzigen kühlen Blick
zum Erstarren. In seinem Inneren verstärkt es
die Energie der Sonne.

Detiene los movimientos del rival con una sola mirada.
Expande la energía solar dentro de su cuerpo.

Può bloccare i movimenti dell’avversario con il solo
sguardo. Amplifica l’energia solare all’interno del
suo corpo.

It can stop its opponents’ movements with just a
glare. It takes in solar energy and boosts
it internally.

にらむだけで　相手の　動きを
止めてしまう。太陽エネルギーを
体内で　増幅させる。
